    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54 platform, maintaining factory tolerances across all critical mechanical systems. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a high-revving valvetrain with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission paired with a torque-sensing M Variable Differential Lock. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, utilizing a meticulously maintained MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for optimal kinematics. Finished in a concours-quality exterior, this vehicle exhibits zero mechanical lash and an immaculate undercarriage, making it a definitive collector-grade driving machine.",
